    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bloodstone Rising</strong> 是一款高强度的 1-4 人合作 FPS Roguelike 游戏，讲述了太空矮人对抗一波又一波不屈不挠的僵尸大军，夺回祖先的王国。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>高强度 FPS Roguelike</strong><br>体验结合 Roguelike 元素的紧张刺激的第一人称射击游戏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>合作模式</strong><br>与朋友组队，共同对抗不断逼近的僵尸大军。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>波次战斗</strong><br>生存下来，面对越来越强大的死敌，每一波敌人都比上一波更致命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338020/extras/219f0f0b16ccfee52b2124e59cfe8a3c.poster.avif?t=1771014590\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338020/extras/219f0f0b16ccfee52b2124e59cfe8a3c.webm?t=1771014590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338020/extras/219f0f0b16ccfee52b2124e59cfe8a3c.mp4?t=1771014590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>采矿与升级</strong><br>在每一波之间采矿，制作升级，提升你的矮人能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338020/extras/afb396010cc17a54a57f6e409fcbf1f2.poster.avif?t=1771014590\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338020/extras/afb396010cc17a54a57f6e409fcbf1f2.webm?t=1771014590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338020/extras/afb396010cc17a54a57f6e409fcbf1f2.mp4?t=1771014590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>深度成长系统</strong><br>解锁强力武器、技能和特权，使每次冒险都变得更强大。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样化武器</strong><br>使用多种受科幻与矮人文化启发的武器，每种武器都有独特的能力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>史诗级 Boss 战斗</strong><br>与巨大的变异僵尸 Boss 战斗，挑战独特的攻击模式和机制。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态环境</strong><br>在废弃的矿洞、地下堡垒和古老的矮人遗迹中展开战斗。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>挑战模式与难度等级</strong><br>在多个难度等级中挑战你的技能。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>程序化多样性</strong><br>每次游戏都有随机事件、强力神器和惊喜等待着你。</p></li></ul>",
